se 4 simulation output is present, reproducible, and internally consistent with Bob's current T581 artifact.\n- Reported metrics are coherent with the simulation logic: the 160 signals come from pairs meeting the spread-threshold logic, not just Bob's 81 explicit arbitrage candidates.\n- Non-blocking implementation note: Dave's script writes canonical artifacts to repo-root `../../output/dave/*`, and identical copies are also present under `../../agents/dave/output/*`. The duplicated paths did not affect correctness in this cycle.\n\n## Decision\n\nApprove T582.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
